reviews.text:
Food was delicious, service was great, very attentive people.
And the $10.00 lobster was on point!
Wonderful experience. We'll definitely be back!
Our fish and fries were excellent! Well seasoned without being spicy hot (sauces available if you like it spicy hot), lightly breaded and not greasy or too...

2nd time here and absolutely recommend. Snow crab additional hit the spot! 

Crawfish and mussels were highlights too!
